  <official_title>A Study to Investigate the Benefit Of Complex Fractionated Atrial Electrogram (CFAE) Ablation in Addition to Circumferential Pulmonary Vein and Linear Ablations in the Treatment of Persistent Atrial Fibrillation. (BOCA)</official_title>
